{
  "stem": "24515.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "In which he has got-- they have got-- permission to enter Panama, Haiti, Shanghai, England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The English visa I was able to procure.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it's a long and complicated story.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I was able to procure it, even though I was only 16, from England.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It came too late, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How did it affect us?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, there's one way, you see?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My mother then urging the emigration.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the next thing, of course, you see, November 18th-- November 10th, a few weeks later, I was told that I had been chosen for the children's transports to go to England.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What I didn't know at the time was that the British were accepting Jews from Germany and Austria, if they could find someone to, so to speak, guarantee them, to have some sort of you know--",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--intention of looking after them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about 100,000 Jews got into England.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And England was, at that time, preparing for war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the British government--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
